@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5

actor User
entity Browser
participant Server
database Database


User -> Browser ++ : navigate to page
Browser -> Server : GET /page
Server -> Database : query data
Database --> Server : data
Server -> Server : render HTML + serialize state
Server --> Browser : full HTML + JS bundle + serialized state
Browser --> User : display pre-rendered HTML\n(page is visible immediately)

Browser -> Browser : load and execute JavaScript
Browser -> Browser : hydrate: attach event listeners\nand restore serialized state
note right of Browser : page is now fully interactive
@enduml
